mic engine for us.\"</strong> <br><br><strong>The time is now to make this a reality! </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Sign the petition and make a difference NOW!\u00a0</strong></p>","targets":[{"name":"Justin Woodson & Hawaii Lawmakers & Leadership","type":"custom"}],"letter_body":"Increase Resources &amp; Support The Filmmaking Industry On Maui","signature_count":31,"image_url":"//d22r54gnmuhwmk.cloudfront.net/photos/7/bg/la/HAbgLaxtUTuKuDe-556x313-cropped.jpg","category":null,"goal":100,"created_at":"2013-12-23T22:07:15Z","end_at":"2014-12-23T23:59:59Z","creator_name":"brad starks","creator_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16309637","organization_name":null,"organization_url":null}